.youtube.com/watch?v=Miwb92eZaJg\" class=\"wiki_link_ext\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Miwb92eZaJg</a><!-- ws:end:WikiTextUrlRule:31 --><br/>\r\n<br/>\r\nAnd, if you&#39;re interested in following Dave, you can do so on his blog: <br/>\r\n<!-- ws:start:WikiTextUrlRule:32:http://www.cognitive-edge.com/blogs/dave/ --><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cognitive-edge.com/blogs/dave/\" class=\"wiki_link_ext\">http://www.cognitive-edge.com/blogs/dave/</a><!-- ws:end:WikiTextUrlRule:32 --> and <br/>\r\n\r\nTwitter: <br/>\r\n<!-- ws:start:WikiTextUrlRule:33:https://twitter.com//snowded --><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com//snowded\" class=\"wiki_link_ext\">https://twitter.com//snowded</a><!-- ws:end:WikiTextUrlRule:33 --><br/>\r\n<br/>\r\n<strong>Live Session with Dave Snowden:</strong><br/>\r\n<br/>\r\nWednesday, January 18 in Collaborate: <br/>\r\n<!-- ws:start:WikiTextUrlRule:34:https://sas.elluminate.com/site/external/launch/meeting.jnlp?sid=2008104&password=M.C5CCF43B9CF818DDB4113D9A1017A8 --><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://sas.elluminate.com/site/external/launch/meeting.jnlp?sid=2008104&password=M.C5CCF43B9CF818DDB4113D9A1017A8\" class=\"wiki_link_ext\">https://sas.elluminate.com/site/external/launch/meeting.jnlp?sid=2008104&password=M.C5CCF43B9CF818DDB4113D9A1017A8</a><!-- ws:end:WikiTextUrlRule:34 --><br/>\r\n<br/>\r\nTime: Eastern time, 2 pm (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=Snowden&iso=20120118T14&p1=250&ah=1\" class=\"wiki_link_ext\">see time zone conversions</a>)\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><keyword db=post;number=20;type=article;format=article_summary;description~week17;all;sort=crdate DESC></p>\r\n\r\n<p><keyword db=post;number=20;type=link;format=link_summary;description~week17;all;sort=crdate DESC></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<keyword db=presentation;format=html;description~week17;all;sort=crdate DESC>','Friday','<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN\"\r\n    \"http